  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Trim, then slice&nbsp;the <strong>spring onions</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bash the <strong>lemongrass</strong> with a rolling pin, cut it <span class=\"text-danger\">[them]</span>&nbsp;down the middle lengthways, remove the tough outer layers (keep them for later!) and chop the <strong>softer inner stem<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Rip/tear the <strong>chestnut&nbsp;mushrooms</strong> (this saves time and creates an interesting texture)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
