            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based deep pan or pot (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped spring onion</strong> and<strong>&nbsp;mushrooms</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>red curry paste,</strong>&nbsp;<strong>curry powder, turmeric&nbsp;</strong>and<strong> chopped&nbsp;lemongrass</strong> and cook for 1-2 min further or until fragrant</p>",
